  <summary date="2019-05-20T21:41:14Z" status="Introduced in House">American Royalties Too Act of 2018

This bill creates a right under copyright entitling artists to a royalty for the sale of their works of visual art, if the work was sold in an auction by someone other than the artist.</summary>
